	        Cloud Security and Content Management: Box Case Study
	    









Cloud Security and Content Management: Box Case Study






Cloud Security and Content Management: Box Case Study





Facebook Like
Tweet
Google +1
LinkedIn
Email



The cloud is inherently unsafe: it decentralizes your company’s data, and creates vague security agreements between your organization and your cloud service provider.
But what if it didn’t have to?
In this case study learn how to secure Box on the cloud, and in doing so yield more benefits than just keeping your data safe, such as:

Reducing overhead
Sharing documents with a simple, secure link
Cutting down on opening risky email attachments
And more




Vendor: 
IBM
